-- Qatar to Start Building First World Cup Stadium, Peninsula Says
-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 2012-06-05T14:42:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/qatar-to-start-building-first-world-cup-stadium-peninsula-says.html
Qatar will begin construction next
year on its Education City stadium, the first to be built for
the 2022 World Cup of soccer,  The Peninsula  reported, citing
Mark Fenwick, director of RFA Iribarren Architects.  To contact the reporter on this story:
